SQL_STMT_U.val: SELECT PRD005.MTOCD , PRD005.MTONAM , PRD005.COL_CD, PRD005.EF_TYP , PRD005.SHA_NO , PRD005.AF_DAT, PRD005.KDLOT FROM PRD005 WHERE PRD005.AF_DAT <> '00000000' AND PRD005.AE_DAT = '00000000' AND PRD005.EFM = 'E' AND OEM_CAT<>'X' AND REP_CAT<>'X' AND PRD005.AF_DAT || TO_CHAR (AF_TIM,'HH24MISS') >=':1' AND PRD005.AF_DAT || TO_CHAR (AF_TIM,'HH24MISS') <=':2' ORDER BY PRD005.MTOCD , PRD005.COL_CD, PRD005.EF_TYP , PRD005.SHA_NO
